name: BUSH FLYING in a FLOATPLANE around Whitehorse, Yukon!
description:
In June last year, I visited beautiful Whitehorse, Yukon, and although I’ve already posted a couple videos from that trip, I wanted to share another unique thing I did while I was there.

As an Alberta resident, I’ve never actually been on a floatplane, and with only a few days to spend in Whitehorse, I figured this would be the best way to see as much as I can!

Enjoy this look at flying in a floatplane around this gorgeous part of Canada!

Alpine Aviation (not sponsored): https://www.alpineaviationyukon.com/
